# seps

Command-line tool to insert separator/header comments in your source files so labels are centered and each line fills up to a character limit.

## Preview 

For example, this:

```js
// @reg Functions
```

becomes:

```js
// ========================================================================= //
//                                 Functions                                 //
// ========================================================================= //
```


